		<div id="comment-375389">
			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<img alt='' src='http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/5a1ef1de93e080ea445884ef3c940f33?s=40&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/5a1ef1de93e080ea445884ef3c940f33?s=80&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' />				<cite class="fn"><a href='http://www.tangentonline.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Dave Truesdale</a></cite> <span class="says">says:</span>			</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->
				
